Body: Top perks you get as CHR token holder https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7vXNwJP6I0I  Top perks you get as CHR token holder:  ORGANIZATIONS Use tokens to: - List campaigns (instead of subscription) - Promote campaigns and advertise them on our live feed Integrate CHERR.IO on external platform - Be listed on our CharityMarketCap  DONORS Use tokens to: - Rate organizations after each fund-raising campaign is completed - Decide where funds from the emergency pool should be spent - Vote and tell the CHERR.IO community if funds from organizations were spent correctly  TOKEN HOLDERS Use tokens to: - Stake a project with CHR tokens, become an ambassador, promote it, take part and reap rewards - Stake CHR tokens and get a percentage of the reward from each completed campaign - Exchange Proof of Charity points for CHR tokens.  CHERR.IO is blockchain solution for charitable donations that aims to put something new in the way charitable, humanitarian and socially responsible organizations operate. With this platform we focus on making transparency and fraud prevention our top priorities, along with features such as enabling the donor confirmation of fund allocation, reward system for all active participants, as well as raising funds with cryptocurrencies and extremely low transaction fees.

Author: aljazstraser
Title: [ANN][ICO]Cherr.ioüçíBLOCKCHAIN SOLUTION FOR CHARITABLE DONATIONSüèÜFH Winner 2018
Body: Hello,  Thank you for your question. I don't know if we can be compared to ACT. We are building a blockchain solution for charitable donations, aiming to open new horizons for the way charitable, humanitarian and socially responsible organizations operate. The platform will opt for optimizing operations, expand outreach, reinforce donors' trust and improve the donation process for charities. Our top focus is fraud prevention and transparency. Alongside this we are aiming to enable decision power for our donors and a reward system for our active participants. We aim to raise funds with cryptocurrencies and thus, enable our donors to experience low transaction fees. CHERR.IO will use a gamification process to engage with a multitude of interested parties willing to both donate and volunteer for others in need.  Check our website at https://www.cherr.io  Also we are getting really good feedback and ratings on ICO listings.  Regards, Aljaz CHERR.IO

Author: aljazstraser
Title: [ANN][ICO]Cherr.ioüçíBLOCKCHAIN SOLUTION FOR CHARITABLE DONATIONSüèÜFH Winner 2018
Body: Cherries have always been loved by many not only because they are sweet and beautiful, but also because they announce the coming of summer. They come in pairs or triplets, tightly bound to their siblings, like our CHEER.IO community is connected within itself and with the rest of the world. Cherry pits are also very resilient, surviving temperatures of -30 degrees C to grow into tall and strong trees that will blossom come spring and bring goodness to the world. CHEER.IO strives to follow the same example and help people in distress return joy and purpose to their lives. Furthermore, like cherries are used for jam, marmalade, desserts and juice, our platform strives to be versatile in the forms of aid and support it can provide to the world  Regards, Aljaz CHERR.IO
